{"id": 1762, "genre": 1000, "title": "促销让人烦，不过哪些你还会看？", "description": "以一种令人愉悦的方式告诉我什么又便宜了，我还是会果断下单的啊。", "record_count": 5685, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170628164343lWoE6X9NeatmqMhI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-28T17:00:49Z", "questions": [{"id": 2510, "title": "促销让人烦，不过哪些你还会看？", "content": "促销让人烦，不过哪些你还会看？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 216366, "content": "真喜欢的品牌，希望在公众号上看到促销推送，这样才能保证第一时间看到", "image": "img/option/option/20170627151601qPB07FHzJmMNDfa9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216367, "content": "随时被促销打扰很烦，但愿意找个不太常用的邮箱收促销邮件，时不时看看", "image": "img/option/option/201706271524378kas2Tm3IJldCRUg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216368, "content": "建一个微博分组，把感兴趣的荐物博主和品牌都放在里面，关注他们的新花样", "image": "img/option/option/20170627153305BYcPAk9jrz61muJ4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216380, "content": "会关注“亚航大促”“餐厅优惠精选”这样的社交网络账号", "image": "img/option/option/20170627152554pDv5qU2bHwzkX6aN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216371, "content": "主要看豆瓣小组之类的论坛，“一起团购”之类的", "image": "img/option/option/201706271527160LNOkyaMq2EVpFJ5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216374, "content": "把“猜你喜欢”和促销推送结合起来，让我看到刚好想买的东西在降价", "image": "img/option/option/20170627152907anNCsD5K0RWZ41gj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216375, "content": "简单直接告诉我什么东西打几折才会看，满减之类的就算了", "image": "img/option/option/201706271530137NwLHdJsKxMfn06E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216370, "content": "在各类“教你花钱”的App上直接订阅感兴趣的品类", "image": "img/option/option/20170627153814qBJOv3l7P2tNzi0w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}